Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:04.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:06.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,when I have a miraculous battle over a crow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:10.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,with Black Phantom Thief, \Nan unexpected rival, what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:18.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.76,0:00:21.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Finally, I'll just say this to you once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:25.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Remember it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:28.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When you come in contact with the audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:31.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,it's the scene of a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:35.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Never be arrogant. Never underestimate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.21,0:00:38.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,See into their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:44.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Give undivided concentration \Nto your fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:47.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is your last advice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:49.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Use every trick you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.62,0:00:51.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's just like Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:56.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,On top of that, never lose \Nyour smile or dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:58.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And at all times...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:02.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...remember your poker face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:41.51,Signs - Thief Title,,0,0,11,,{\a1}{\fad(0,100)}Midnight Crow (Part One): \NThe Name is Corbeau the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:20.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Disappointing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:26.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I came prepared with two \Nmore back-up plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:29.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How anticlimactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:34.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, Hakuba took a leave \Nof absence to travel abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:38.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And with Inspector Nakamori \Nin bed with a bad cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:40.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,this is a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:46.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The world's biggest black diamond,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,the Midnight Crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I should be able to pick this lock\N in less than a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:54.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:58.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My hands aren't moving the way I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:02.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And it's really cold in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:05.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The old man was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:07.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:11.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...has a weakness to cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:14.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hakuba and Inspector?! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:17.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Get him, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:27.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:32.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You let down your guard because you \Nthought I was home sick in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:33.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Never underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:37.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My cop nature kicked that cold\N to the curb after a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your plan worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:44.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I only told Aoko I had a cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:46.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How did Kid know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We caught Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right! Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:01.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wrong! I'm not Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't know when to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:09.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:11.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That face...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:13.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:22.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-You're Oshima from Squad C!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:26.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kid put a mask of you on my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:28.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...a-and escaped out the ceiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:30.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Son of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After him, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:37.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,U-Um, what should I do about these handcuffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:39.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who cares?! Figure something out yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:42.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:47.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My double disguise worked like a charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:51.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Putting one of the investigators to sleep\N just in case was the right move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:58.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But it looks like I'll have to reschedule \Nto get another shot at that jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:01.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hakuba's watching it like a hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:04.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And what the inspector said bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:07.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The old man was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:10.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:15.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Did the plan go smoothly for the \Ninspector tonight because of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:17.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:18.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:26.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:31.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Staying in Kid's outfit in these circumstances\N could be easily misconstrued.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:32.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Please change into something else right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:37.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,G-Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:44.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito, did you see the news on the net?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:47.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It says "Complete Defeat \Nfor Kid the Phantom Thief"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:48.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:55.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Cheers and jeers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:06:58.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who toasts with ginger ale?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:01.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why do you have band-aids \Nall over your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:08.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The price I paid for using strong adhesive \Non that second mask so it wouldn't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That aside, Jii-chan, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:18.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Apparently, there's an old man \Ngiving advice to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:19.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:25.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've heard that Senior Adviser Suzuki \Ndoesn't have anything to do with this jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:27.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, not that rich old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:29.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Harry Nezu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:34.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's a famous magic trick buster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:38.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It says the police drove Kid off this time\N thanks to Nezu-san's advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:40.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Magic trick buster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. His nickname's "the Hedgehog."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:47.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He made his name debunking \Nfraudulent spirit mediums.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:52.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems magicians all over the world regularly \Nchallenge him, but are soon "busted."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:55.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This says he's coming to Japan today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:59.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then maybe the old man's going \Nto meet Inspector Nakamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:00.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then this is a gift for the inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:05.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:07.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,To celebrate driving Kid away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:12.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's gonna meet somebody famous, so you \Nwant him to have a little style, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:15.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hari!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:20.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you in Japan to help \Narrest Kid the Phantom Thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:24.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief... \NThe brat in the white suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:25.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:30.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Brat? I've been on his trail for 18 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:33.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He looks like a youngster to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:35.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even his name is "Kid."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's a fancy necktie pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:46.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...a present from my daughter's friend, to \Ncelebrate us driving away Kid the other night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:50.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems your daughter has a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:54.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Although I'd say he has bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So the advance notice was for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:04.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}I was afraid he'd realized there's a \Ncamera and mic planted in the tie pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:04.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, he sent it to the police \Ndepartment two days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:07.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,saying he was going to try again \Ntonight at midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:12.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And does he know you're going to change \Nthe exhibition room of the jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:16.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. I went out of my way to \Nannounce it on TV last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:18.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't think he knows \Nthe exact room, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:23.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now we just have to wait for him \Nto show up, as brazen as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:28.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inside the mousetrap I've prepared...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,M-Minus 10 degrees Celsius!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:37.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is this floor that cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:41.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. That was my instruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:45.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Will we really be able \Nto catch him like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:47.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll work for the brat in white.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:51.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He got away last time \Nbecause it wasn't cold enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:58.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Deceiving the eyes with skilled fingers \Nis what a magician does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:04.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A phantom thief who uses magic becomes a \Nbabe in the woods if he can't use those fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:06.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Figures they would go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:10.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,B-But it's also hard for us cops \Nto catch Kid in this cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:15.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right. Your bodies will be too \Nsluggish from the cold to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But as for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll stay toasty-warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:22.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:27.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...I'll just sneak into the building before \Nmidnight, impersonate that old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:30.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:34.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I couldn't care less \Nabout that brat in white.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:39.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But didn't we make it this cold\N in order to catch Kid...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:42.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My prey isn't the one in white...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:44.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...but the one in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:47.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The one in black?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:53.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This morning, my father, the commissioner, \Nreceived another advance notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:59.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Tonight at midnight, please forgive \Nmy rudeness when I take my black jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:02.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Corbeau the Phantom Thief"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:03.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,P-Phantom Thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:05.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Corbeau?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:08.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Corbeau" means crow in French.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:11.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's why he refers to the \NMidnight Crow as "his."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:14.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And crows do like shiny objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:18.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I received the same missive last week,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:22.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,which is why I've come \Nto my father's homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:26.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,B-But who is this Corbeau?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:29.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A phantom thief who's been \Nactive in Las Vegas lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:33.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Scattering countless crow feathers \Nat the scene of the crime is his M.O.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But the surprising thing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:37.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,is that he looks just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just like...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:40.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Like what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A black feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:58.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:00.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who are you supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:20.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Considering the outfit, my guess is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:23.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...you're a fan of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:26.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:31.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's my line...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:34.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...Corbeau the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:38.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's changing his voice, but it feels like\N I've heard it before somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:40.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:44.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I have a feeling\N I've seen you once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Once before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:51.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Was it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:57.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You've devoted yourself to thieving in Japan \Nwhile cosplaying in an outfit like my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:00.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I believe your name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...Child the Robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:09.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And you've only just started being active!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:11.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're the one who's copying me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I suffered from an illness \Nfor quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:18.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After healing up, I was just \Nwaiting for the right moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:22.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Waiting to take revenge for my \Nfellow apprentice, Toichi Kuroba,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:26.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,who was murdered eight years ago\N at a magic show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:32.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I repurposed this stage outfit\N he left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's different from your aping the style.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:42.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Aside from that, it seems you've got \Nportable heating pads stuck all over your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:46.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so the fact that you're about to dive \Ninto a trap prepared by that hedgehog
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:49.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,tells me you're a thoughtless lightweight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:56.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shall we make a wager?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:14:02.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonight I intend to melt into the darkness,\N hiding all traces of myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:08.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and then make that black jewel, the Midnight \NCrow, my own, without even touching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:12.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then, if you can't understand how I did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:16.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,you'll have to be a good sport and \Nretire as a professional thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:21.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There is no need for two ghosts\N of Toichi Kuroba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:23.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,S-Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:37.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, if I see through \Nyour trick, then {\i1}you{\i0} retire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:39.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Two phantom thieves...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:56.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No problem, no matter how many there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:15:00.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We just have to take the jewel \Nfrom the one who steals it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:03.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The Stone of Life... Pandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:06.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?! Kid's not coming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:16.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're sure you got that mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:21.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. It just came to the department. \NIt said, "Tonight, I'll just be watching."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:26.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It was rerouted through an overseas server, \Nso we couldn't pinpoint the original sender,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:31.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but the mail had Kid's usual trademark, \Nso we believe it really came from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:36.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems he's curious about \NCorbeau the Phantom Thief, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:45.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Corbeau, Corvette, whatever, he's \Nthrown cold water on the festivities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:55.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks to him, we've lost \Nthe chance to catch Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:08.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It isn't hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:21.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey! There's no need to touch that pedestal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:23.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,P-Pedestal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:28.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I made it in my country and \Nhad it brought here to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:31.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's my secret weapon against Corbeau.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,At a glance, it looks like \Nan ordinary pedestal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But when I release the safety like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:44.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,if there are any objects nearby, \Nsharp blades spring out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:50.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...and it rotates at a high speed \Nthat can rip anything to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:56.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course, the case is \Nmade of ultra-dense glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:17:00.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And the black fabric \Nthe jewel lies upon is engineered
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:02.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,to be stab-proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:05.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:18.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:22.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It certainly is the genuine black \Ndiamond, the Midnight Crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:28.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That case has a weird contraption, \Nbut it's not locked...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:35.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori, the key...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:37.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:40.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:44.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're going to wear a gas mask\N and sit atop this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:46.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,holding on to the handles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:57.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:18:01.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,As long as you hold on to those handles,\N the case can't be opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori! It's almost time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:06.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:10.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, Corbeau the Phantom Thief,\N you night bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Appear from anywhere you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:16.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You should be the one sitting on the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:19.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,F-From the ceiling vent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Crow feathers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:37.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Corbeau is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:41.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector! Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:43.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll die before I let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:06.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-It stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What about the jewel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:12.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I held on the whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:17.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:19.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A coin in its place...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:24.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A word etched into it... Corbeau!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:26.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:28.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How could he do it without opening the case?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:30.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That really is magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is this the time to be impressed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:40.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There are words on the bottom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:44.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Next time I'll be back \Nto take the real thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:46.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-The real thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:51.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a trick I often pull \Nin my confrontations with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:56.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I had a strange foreboding, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:59.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So I switched it out with a fake \Nright before the appointed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:04.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Although it seems he saw through \Nmy bait-and-switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:11.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Still, even if it was a fake, \Nhe really did steal the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:15.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And if we don't know how he did it,\N maybe next time, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:20.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The main point is that our field of vision \Nwas obscured by those crow feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:22.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Being distracted by that was our downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:26.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time, we can't afford to neglect \Nthe ventilation shafts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:29.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:33.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get this coin over to the crime lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:34.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:38.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Although I'm sure he won't have \Nleft his fingerprints on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:46.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He melted into the darkness, \Nerasing all traces of himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:49.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and stole the jewel without touching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:52.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Corbeau the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:21:00.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Although this is no time to be impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:05.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How did he take the jewel \Nwithout opening the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:10.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If it was magic, there would've been some \Ndevice in the case, covered by the black cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:15.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I'm also curious about his identity, \Nsince he called Dad his "fellow apprentice".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:20.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And Jii-chan said he can't recall \Nanyone referring to Dad by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:25.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, guess I'll head home \Nand search the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:30.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? The lights are on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:35.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:42.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kaito! Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:45.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,M-Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.82,0:21:54.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,An unexpected person showed up, \Nbut this is no time to be shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:22:00.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna settle my showdown \Nwith Corbeau the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:04.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The illusion must go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:24.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, I think I'll relax \Nand do this final preview alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:28.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Still, Corbeau the Phantom Thief... \NHow the heck did he do that trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:32.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The fact that he picked a fight with me \Nshows just how strong he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:35.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I can't be defeated here \Nand have a good reason for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:38.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.23,0:23:42.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,Midnight Crow (Part Two): \NClash! White or Black?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:42.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The last episode! "Midnight Crow (Part Two): \NClash! White or Black?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:46.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.03,0:23:48.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't miss the last illusion!
